A cozy living room scene on Christmas Eve in Studio Ghibli style, featuring a wide-eyed young boy in pajamas kneeling eagerly beside a decorated Christmas tree, hands clasped together in hopeful anticipation. A plate of cookies and milk sits nearby. Through a frosted window, snow falls gently. A gaming console box wrapped in shiny red paper with a golden bow peeks out from under the tree, catching warm lamplight. The room glows with soft amber tones from string lights, casting magical shadows. A plush armchair holds a sleeping cat curled contentedly. Pine garlands drape the mantelpiece where stockings hang. The boy's expression perfectly captures that mixture of desperate hope and childlike wonder unique to Christmas morning anticipation.
